</li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The Personal Law of the Mahommedans: According to All the Schools, Syed Ameer Ali, WH Allen &amp; Company, London, pp. 299-300</span>
</li>
